---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<Layout title="Child Care Resource & Referral | Upfront" description="We are dedicated to supporting CCR&Rs in their mission to support families and childcare providers.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        Supporting CCR&R with Automated ECE Data
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-brand-gray max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        We are dedicated to supporting Child Care Resource and Referral Agencies (CCR&Rs) in their mission to support families and childcare providers. Our user-friendly platform enables user-friendly childcare search for families, robust call referral intakes, and seamless provider training and coaching case management.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solutions -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-brand-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4 text-center">
        ECE Data to Support Families and Providers
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-8 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Upfront's reporting and dashboards provide valuable insights into family search behavior, empowering agencies to make data-driven decisions and improve operational efficiency.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">Modern Family Search</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm mb-4">
            Consolidate every data source such as Licensing, Quality, Provider Data, and CCMS into a single database for families to access in a user-friendly search website.
          </p>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Integrated with Upfront's innovative Vacancy Data Collection, families can find real-time openings in nearby programs.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">Automated Call Referral</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm mb-4">
            Help and track families find up-to-date childcare and ECE providers filterable by location, price, vacancies, hours, and other fields with our SOC II certified platform.
          </p>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Automated surveys go out to families post-referral to track success.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">Seamless Coaching and Training</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm mb-4">
            Manage Technical Assistance/Coaching with tools that make planning, tracking, and improving easier than ever.
          </p>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Administer and connect childcare providers with professional development by publishing, managing, and tracking courses.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-8 text-center">
        Hear from Our Customers
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-teal/30 mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z" />
          </svg>
          <blockquote class="text-lg text-brand-navy mb-4">
            "Technology should make lives easier — and that's exactly what Upfront does for Maryland families."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-gray font-medium">Executive Director, Maryland Family Network</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-teal/30 mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z" />
          </svg>
          <blockquote class="text-lg text-brand-navy mb-4">
            "Upfront was a partner on every level — taking families, providers, and data into consideration for every decision."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-gray font-medium">Founder, Operation Child Care</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-brand-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">
        Learn about North Carolina's New Automated Data Platform
      </h2>
      <a href="/case-studies/north-carolina" class="inline-flex items-center text-brand-teal font-medium hover:underline">
        Read the Case Study
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABanner />
</Layout>
